name: PARASITIC OPPXRTUNISM
description: Congratulations my fellow viral load collectors, Why not tag along in a lesser way. The X is can mean a lot of things, solve for X, 10 nfts, the signature left by those without signatures. This time has been hard for us all, and I want to wish us all a happy "You Received an offer" until the end of time. This was sent to the top 100 fans (minus myself and the auction house) of the SARS-COV-2 contract, most of which had collected all 10 tokens at the time.
